果他独自读到这样的信息，这真的会把他推向崩溃边缘。” CBS称，这不是谷歌AI聊天机器人第一次被曝光在回复用户询问时给出可能有害的回答。7月，记者发现，“Gemini”就各种健康问题给出了错误的、可能致命的信息，例如它建议人们“每天至少吃一块小石子”以补充维生素和矿物质。谷歌当时回应称，它已经对“Gemini”就健康问题回复时包含的讽刺和幽默网站信息进行了限制。 （参考来源：https://weibo.com/1686546714/5102366057565612）"},"attached_info":"CkEI64L46sa2ueYcEAMaCTExMTg5MTM3NyCWgPG5BjAAOOEGQBpyCjQ1NzMzMjE3NDZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"热度累计中","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-2dc54bf0a32e420bae5e3689fb4b5240_r.jpg?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"27_1732455178.810956","card_id":"Q_4738035686","target":{"id":4738035686,"title":"丑画像和「完美伴侣」争议后，李行亮努力哄麦琳却激化矛盾，吐槽她难哄，麦琳究竟想要怎样的「完美道歉」？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/4738035686","type":"question","created":1732169710,"answer_count":180,"follower_count":258,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1793,115410,2249723,3743562,3754367],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"麦琳真的太难哄了！李行亮用心了重新画了一幅漫画给麦琳，麦琳却不满意，觉得敷衍，武艺和Papi酱等人看了都忍不住吐槽：“姐！你到底要什么啊？” 麦琳是真的很难哄好，李行亮其实真的很用心的在和她道歉，为她准备惊喜了，但她却很不满意，一脸的不高兴。李行亮麦琳 难哄 综艺风波引热议"},"attached_info":"CkEI64L46sa2ueYcEAMaCTExMTkyNDI2NyDun/u5BjAAOIICQBtyCjQ3MzgwMzU2ODZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"热度累计中","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-eb9b7061cb6766cb9e0700d7d34af07a_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"28_1732455178.811316","card_id":"Q_921303118","target":{"id":921303118,"title":"杨志自己设计的护送生辰纲的方式是不是一开始就是错的？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/921303118","type":"question","created":1728949842,"answer_count":43,"follower_count":84,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[4364,3